					<div id="elementor-tab-content-1251" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="1" role="region" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-1251"><p><strong><u>*Step Number 1:</u></strong> <strong>Install the Downloader</strong> (if you have the Downloader already installed you can Skip this Step and install the app in Step Number 4)</p><ol><li>You need to be on the home screen of FireStick</li></ol><p>Select<strong>FIND</strong></p><p></p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image2.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image2.png" /></noscript></p><ol start="2"><li>Now, click <strong>Search<br /></strong><strong><br /></strong><img decoding="async"  data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image1.png" class="alignnone lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" class="alignnone" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image1.png" /></noscript></li></ol><ol start="3"><li>In the Search window, search for the app called<strong><strong>Downloader</strong></strong></li></ol><p>This is the app through which we will sideload IPTV APP on FireStick</p><p>Follow the instructions that appear on the screen and install this app</p><p><br /><strong><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image3.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image3.png" /></noscript></strong></p><p></p><ol start="4"><li>You should now see<strong>Downloader </strong>under the <strong>APPS &amp; GAMES</strong> section. Go ahead and <strong>click it</strong>.<br /><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image4.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image4.png" /></noscript></li></ol><p>And Continue installing the Downloader ..</p><p><strong><u>Step 2 : If Developer Options not available follow this step if not just skip it .</u></strong></p><p>5- Now, the next option you will access is <strong>Developer Options</strong></p><p><strong><br /><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" /></noscript></noscript><br /></strong></p><p><strong><u>N.B:</u></strong><strong><u> If you cant see Developer Options, </u></strong><strong><u>follow the next steps :</u></strong></p><p>Click<strong>About</strong>(only if you <strong>DO NOT</strong>see Developer Options on this screen).</p><p> </p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image6.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image6.png" /></noscript></p><p>Click on your <strong>Fire TV Stick </strong>quickly <strong>7</strong> times.</p><p> </p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image7.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image7.png" /></noscript></p><p></p><p>You will see a notification at the bottom saying<strong>No need, you are already a developer.</strong>Thats it, you have enabled Developer Options.<br /><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image8.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image8.png" /></noscript></p><p></p><p>Press the back button once or go back to <strong>Settings</strong> &gt; <strong>My Fire TV </strong>and you will now see Developer Options.</p><p>Now you can go into Developer Options and enable Apps from Unknown Sources to sideload APKs on your FireStick device ,</p><p><strong><u>*Step Number 3:</u></strong> <strong>Enable install unknown apps</strong></p><p>1- Get back to the home screen and select<strong>Settings</strong></p><p><strong><u><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image9.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image9.png" /></noscript></u></strong></p><p></p><p> 2- Within Settings, go to the option<strong>My Fire TV</strong>and open it</p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image10.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image10.png" /></noscript></p><p></p><p>3- Now, the next option you will access is<strong>Developer Options</strong></p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image5.png" /></noscript></noscript></p><p></p><p>4- On the window that opens next, go ahead and click on<strong>Install Unknown Apps</strong></p><p><strong>Note:</strong><em>If you still have the older version of the FireStick interface, click Apps from Unknown Sources</em></p><p><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image11.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image11.png" /></noscript></p><p></p><p>5- Turn the option ON for the Downloader app<br /><img decoding="async" data-src="https://hunotv.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image12.png" class="lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" /><noscript><img decoding="async" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/template/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image12.png" /></noscript></p><p></p><p>Once you have enabled Apps from Unknown Sources, you may start installing the iptv app on FireStick.</p><p><strong><u>*Step Number 4:</u></strong> <strong>install The Server Player ( The App )</strong></p><p><strong> </strong></p><p>Now that the Downloader app is enabled, open it and dismiss any prompts that appear.</p><p>2 &#8211; Type this Code: <strong>834339 </strong>on the URL textbo